        <updateDate>2022-07-04T19:41:17Z</updateDate>
        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Securing America's Ports of Entry Act of 2022</b></p> <p>This bill requires U.S. Customs and Border Protection (CBP) to increase the number of CBP officers to specified levels. If CBP does not adequately increase personnel, the Government Accountability Office must report on CBP hiring practices.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
